cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.MM 

The paper deals with zero-shot learning, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). It also involves the use of semantic features and word vectors, which are common in natural language processing (cs.CL) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper evaluates its proposed method on visual data, which falls under multimedia (cs.MM).
